description: YouTube just deleted my last video where I did nothing but ASK QUESTIONS regarding COVID-19. Add this as more ammo to possibly used in the future lawsuit against the tech tyrants we will hopefully be filing this week. THE TRUTH IS A FORCE OF NATURE & NOTHING CAN STOP WHAT IS COMING.
